    <center><big><strong>Self-avatars in Immersive Technology</strong></big></center>
    <center><small>Monday, 29 March, 2021 - 10:30, WEST UTC+1</small></center>
    
    <center><small>Session Chair: <b style="font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; color: black;">Ming Lin</b></small></center>
    
    
    
    
