    <center><big><strong>B(l)ending Realities</strong></big></center>
    <center><small>Wednesday, 31 March, 2021 - 11:00, WEST UTC+1</small></center>
    
    <center><small>Session Chair: <b style="font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; color: black;">Maud Marchal</b></small></center>
    
    
    
    
